WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:25.080
Today we are going to worship

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:32.920
the Devi, we call her Amba,

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:37.480
and by many other names.

00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:47.160
She is the last, we should say, the ''residual power''

00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:51.120
When she has done everything

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:55.080
she becomes the Kundalini

00:00:55.280 --> 00:01:01.200
and settles in the triangular bone of yours.

00:01:02.880 --> 00:01:06.880
This is the Mooladhara Chakra.

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:12.960
But actually she is expressed

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:16.840
more on the left side,

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:23.560
because that time she is purely the Amba.

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:35.000
This left side is a very, very important

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:40.320
thing for all the human beings.

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:48.880
lf you have no left side, you cannot balances to begin with.

00:01:49.240 --> 00:01:54.320
And it is said that

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:00.080
she gives you a real personality

00:02:01.440 --> 00:02:05.240
of a Sahaja Yogi.

00:02:11.040 --> 00:02:17.160
That is, your left side, if it is weak,

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:22.160
then you have to worship her;

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:30.400
and request her that ''Please enrich our left side''.

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:34.920
By enriching your left side,

00:02:35.320 --> 00:02:38.920
what she does, she is a comforter,

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:45.240
So, what does she give you? First of all, she makes you rest.

00:02:45.880 --> 00:02:49.200
It is said that she makes you rest.

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:53.960
That is, she makes you sleep.

00:02:54.920 --> 00:02:57.920
lf you are too much thinking about future

00:02:58.120 --> 00:03:03.920
and you are so much indulging into the futuristic planning,

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:06.920
you have some problems;

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:10.840
but the best thing is if you can sleep,

00:03:11.320 --> 00:03:14.560
then it is a great comfort,

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:18.360
it is a very great comfort to you that you can sleep

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:22.880
and that you can take some rest.

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:31.680
Without her you cannot sleep: absence of her, you cannot sleep.

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:37.880
So sleeping is a very important function

00:03:38.080 --> 00:03:43.240
of the body, which is brought forth by the left side.

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:46.960
That's why we worship her,

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:51.360
because she should give us rest.

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:56.040
She's the one who gives you peace;

00:03:56.640 --> 00:04:00.760
She's the one who

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:06.400
gives you also illusions,

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:11.080
called as Bhranti.

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:16.720
She gives you all the artistic talents,

00:04:17.320 --> 00:04:20.080
she protects you.

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:25.400
But this part that is she is

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:30.280
creating illusions for you

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:33.640
that's very, very important.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:40.880
Because those people who are against Divine,

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:50.280
who are trying to be away from the reality,

00:04:50.760 --> 00:04:53.880
she creates illusions for them.

00:04:54.440 --> 00:04:58.800
So she separates you from those people,

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:01.320
while you know the reality

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:06.440
and all such people who are

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:14.240
troubling or trying to destroy her work

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:20.520
She is the one who creates illusions.

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:26.160
She is the one who resides as the Kundalini.

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:35.120
So we can say that part of her is the Kundalini,

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:42.200
but another part that she has

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:47.960
is the one which resides in the left side.

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:54.960
Now there are seven

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:02.760
levels

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:07.840
which she resides.

00:06:09.200 --> 00:06:15.240
Once you start enjoying her on the first level,

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:21.280
then She has all these qualities described to you.

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:24.840
That She is peace,

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:29.920
She is the one who gives you love,

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:35.160
She is the one who creates

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:39.920
all the beautiful things for you.

00:06:41.640 --> 00:06:43.680
She is the Mother.

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:49.200
And what She expects you is to enjoy her protection,

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:52.960
enjoy her love and be always

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:58.400
under her complete protection.

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:07.920
So this is a very important part of her work.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:13.440
And the second one is that She is the Kundalini.

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:18.360
So She also acts on seven levels.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:24.920
Seven levels She moves, we can say horizontally,

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:33.040
and seven levels she moves upward.

00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:37.840
And all these seven levels, on both of the sides.

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:43.560
She does tremendous work for us.

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:49.400
How she protects us through these seven levels, is like this,

00:07:49.800 --> 00:07:54.720
that even if you start going towards the left side,

00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:59.000
there are seven Deities

00:07:59.320 --> 00:08:03.880
which try to throw you back into normalcy.

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:09.360
There are Shankini, Dhankini, these are the names.

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:17.280
And by that you try to come to normal conditions.

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:21.920
Now for example, many psychosomatic diseases

00:08:22.320 --> 00:08:28.160
which come to us, like cancer and so many others;

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:33.240
psychosomatic means it is physical

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:37.960
as well as it is emotional.

00:08:38.680 --> 00:08:42.000
So these psychosomatic troubles

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:45.960
start coming from the left side.

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:50.400
Sometimes you are too much on the right side,

00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:54.800
then suddenly you are thrown to the left side, suddenly.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:59.080
And then the movement like a pendulum, you can go any far.

00:08:59.560 --> 00:09:03.080
But there are seven powers on the left-hand side

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:08.360
which protect you from getting into these diseases;

00:09:08.680 --> 00:09:13.040
also reducing

00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:19.240
their intensity.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:27.200
So at one time, she is the one who is peace giving,

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:33.680
she is the one who looks after you and protects you,

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:43.120
and she is the one who saves you from psychosomatic diseases.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:49.200
ls a very powerful entity.

00:09:50.920 --> 00:09:55.840
lf she was not there l don't know what would have happened.

00:09:56.080 --> 00:10:00.200
So we should worship her within ourselves.

00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:04.840
We should respect her, and understand her;

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:08.520
she is your Mother.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:13.480
As Kundalini she is your particular Mother.

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:19.120
She is the one, Amba,

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:23.880
who gives you your second birth.

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:30.240
And as the left side

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:38.640
goddess she gives you

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:43.120
a very good support in your ascent.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.560
A very good support in your ascent.

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:51.120
Without her you could not balance yourself.

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:55.000
This goes too far sometimes

00:10:55.480 --> 00:11:01.240
when people are too much on the right side.

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:05.720
Then they get diseases which are very funny.

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:09.280
They can get heart-attack, they can get paralysis.

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:13.840
They also get the right side completely paralyzed.

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:17.920
They can't walk, they can't lift themselves.

00:11:18.400 --> 00:11:22.240
This is too much of right side movement.

00:11:22.520 --> 00:11:26.800
So then she is the one

00:11:27.360 --> 00:11:33.280
who makes you feel bad about it.

00:11:33.960 --> 00:11:39.120
She is the one who suggests that you give up your right side

00:11:40.160 --> 00:11:44.920
and take more to the left side.

00:11:45.400 --> 00:11:47.720
So that doesn't mean that right side,

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:51.840
if it is cured by the left side,  it is very good.

00:11:52.040 --> 00:11:56.920
For example, a person who is very arrogant, egotistical,

00:11:57.680 --> 00:12:03.720
such a man may become absolutely docile,

00:12:04.800 --> 00:12:11.000
and people might think he is cured. No. He is on the left side.

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:17.360
Though he has become docile, still he is not normal.

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:24.160
Still he is very much wrong because he is on the left side.

00:12:25.400 --> 00:12:31.680
On the left side one starts getting many diseases like schizophrenia

00:12:31.920 --> 00:12:35.320
on the upper level of this group.

00:12:36.520 --> 00:12:40.920
This side these same seven centers

00:12:41.240 --> 00:12:45.440
act to give you very serious troubles.

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:50.880
One of them is that people become schizophrenic.

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:54.120
It can be cured;

00:12:54.480 --> 00:13:00.480
it can be cured if you can move that person to the center.

00:13:01.520 --> 00:13:04.880
And by Kundalini awakening you can do it.

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:10.000
Then people also become mad, lunatic.

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:15.200
But all the troubles of the right side disappear.

00:13:15.800 --> 00:13:18.320
Such people who have moved to the left side

00:13:18.520 --> 00:13:22.160
won't have liver problems.

00:13:22.880 --> 00:13:24.640
They might have enlarged liver,

00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:27.240
but over-active liver they won't have.

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:33.200
They won't have other symptoms like asthma, heart attack.

00:13:34.960 --> 00:13:38.800
They cannot have heart attack. They'll give heart attacks to others

00:13:39.160 --> 00:13:42.800
but they themselves don't get heart attacks.

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:46.280
So this

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:51.200
sudden movement of your attention into the left side

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:55.800
is all the time guarded by these seven entities,

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:58.520
or goddesses,who look after you.

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:02.800
But still if you go on with it:

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:06.920
for example you go to the false gurus;

00:14:07.480 --> 00:14:10.560
then what do the false gurus do?

00:14:10.880 --> 00:14:14.800
They put you to your left side.

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:17.880
They'll give you a name, some name,

00:14:18.160 --> 00:14:21.320
it could be the name of a servant, or anyone

00:14:21.920 --> 00:14:26.240
whom they have captured and whom they are looking after

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:31.880
as a kind of a possession for others.

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:37.160
This is tantrika, they people possess

00:14:37.480 --> 00:14:41.040
the spirits of these dead people

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:45.360
and use them to entice you.

00:14:45.800 --> 00:14:48.960
So when you start

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:53.800
getting into the left side by any means,

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:56.960
you can get it by worrying too much,

00:14:57.400 --> 00:15:01.880
you can get it by feeling very sorry for something,

00:15:02.360 --> 00:15:05.920
or crying, weeping, anything,

00:15:06.320 --> 00:15:12.440
then your right side problems disappear.

00:15:13.200 --> 00:15:18.440
That is why you do it. But it goes too far.

00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:21.960
The right side problems are, if they are cured,

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:25.440
you get the left side problems which are much more dangerous.

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:30.800
l told you all kinds of psychosomatic diseases,

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:34.200
l don't want to give the list to frighten you,

00:15:34.400 --> 00:15:40.280
but they all come from the left side.

00:15:41.800 --> 00:15:48.000
Now, because the right side is a sort of completely

00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:53.040
cured, as they say, people think that it is a very good idea

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:56.360
to get possessed by some spirit.

00:15:56.800 --> 00:15:59.440
So these false gurus, what they do,

00:15:59.680 --> 00:16:07.640
they master these dead spirits.

00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:12.520
How? l mean, they know how to do it;

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:16.200
l need not tell you, you are not going to do it.

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:22.840
And they master it and they tell you that ''You take this name''.

00:16:24.880 --> 00:16:29.920
You start taking the name of some sort of a God-knows-what.

00:16:30.640 --> 00:16:34.640
They don't tell that you take the name of any incarnation,

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:38.040
but they'll tell you ''Take the name of Ram''.

00:16:38.680 --> 00:16:40.440
Ram's name is not taken like that,

00:16:40.640 --> 00:16:45.000
it has to be Shri Ram, Shri Krishna, Shri Mataji.

00:16:45.320 --> 00:16:48.880
So they never put Shri, they just tell you ''Take these names'',

00:16:49.320 --> 00:16:54.160
and by these names what happens is that you go

00:16:54.800 --> 00:17:00.160
to the left side because of these dead spirits, they capture you.

00:17:02.240 --> 00:17:03.960
There are dead spirits on the left side

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:07.920
and there are dead spirits on the right side.

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:14.400
lf they are on the right side they are very ambitious people,

00:17:14.880 --> 00:17:21.720
and they try to capture you. It is a very

00:17:25.480 --> 00:17:31.240
frightening explanation of the whole thing.

00:17:32.080 --> 00:17:36.360
Once they capture you, if you go to the right side,

00:17:36.680 --> 00:17:41.840
you get all right side ''qualities'', you are not normal.

00:17:43.280 --> 00:17:49.400
Sometimes you feel you are going in the air somewhere,

00:17:49.800 --> 00:17:54.960
you have seen something which you would normally not see.

00:17:55.480 --> 00:18:00.240
Like two Americans came to see me and they were journalists.

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:03.560
So l asked them ''Why are you here?''

00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:06.800
They said ''Mother, you make us like Harishchandra''.

00:18:07.000 --> 00:18:11.000
There was one fellow called Harishchandra who was a journalist.

00:18:11.600 --> 00:18:14.400
l said, ''But, like him?''

00:18:14.720 --> 00:18:20.960
Because he used to travel in the air, and he used to get news,

00:18:21.360 --> 00:18:27.320
like he would tell, about what is happening in some part

00:18:39.680 --> 00:18:46.000
some part of Bombay

00:18:46.520 --> 00:18:48.760
like we have a Juboo Beach

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:55.000
So one day in the newspaper it came out what happened at Juboo Beach

00:19:01.560 --> 00:19:04.920
and his name was there,

00:19:05.280 --> 00:19:10.240
the one who is the correspondent was Mr Harishchandra.

00:19:11.600 --> 00:19:14.760
So, how did Harishchandra tell you my name?

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:20.960
l cured him, while you want to get into his trouble?

00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:26.200
So we want to have this ''astral travel'', Americans,

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:29.760
''For what?'' ''Because we are journalists

00:19:29.960 --> 00:19:32.280
and we'll know so much about everything

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:34.920
we want to travel all over''.

00:19:35.200 --> 00:19:37.080
l said ''This l don't do''.

00:19:37.520 --> 00:19:42.480
lf you are doing astral travel, of course l can reduce it .

00:19:42.920 --> 00:19:47.280
So all these gurus had mastered

00:19:47.480 --> 00:19:49.920
also this art of astral travel,

00:19:50.240 --> 00:19:55.960
controlling some dead spirits who were right sided.

00:19:57.440 --> 00:20:03.160
So right sided spirits are very ambitious

00:20:03.600 --> 00:20:06.960
and they do all kinds of healings,

00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:11.760
and all kinds of predictions,

00:20:12.080 --> 00:20:16.000
because they are futuristic.

00:20:16.520 --> 00:20:20.320
Sometimes they know, sometimes they don't know.

00:20:20.720 --> 00:20:25.240
But it is all coming from a wrong source;

00:20:26.080 --> 00:20:31.040
so getting into that trap is not a very good thing.

00:20:31.920 --> 00:20:34.800
lf somebody is possessed like that,

00:20:35.000 --> 00:20:39.280
then such a person starts doing all kinds of wrong things.

00:20:39.880 --> 00:20:44.240
Like it will try to grab your house,

00:20:44.440 --> 00:20:50.200
to grab your money, to deceive you,

00:20:51.640 --> 00:20:54.400
run away with your wife, all kinds of things

00:20:54.680 --> 00:20:57.040
which are absolutely wrong.

00:20:57.400 --> 00:21:03.200
Because the influence of the right side increases with it.

00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:08.600
Also there are some drugs, when you take them,

00:21:09.120 --> 00:21:11.800
like LSD and all that,

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:16.920
you go to the right side and then you start seeing colours,

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:20.120
and people think it is a very great thing to see colours,

00:21:20.320 --> 00:21:23.160
because normally you don't see colours.

00:21:23.440 --> 00:21:26.520
They don't know basically what is wrong with them.

00:21:26.880 --> 00:21:29.080
But basically what is wrong with them is that

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:34.400
there is a bhoot, there is some sort of a ghost

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:38.800
which is very right sided, has gone into their being

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:42.080
and trying to work it out.

00:21:44.120 --> 00:21:47.200
But the left side bhoots are different then.

00:21:47.800 --> 00:21:52.960
They are sly and they teach you peevish things.

00:21:54.280 --> 00:22:00.680
They may also try to entice you

00:22:01.600 --> 00:22:07.400
to such an extent that a person can tell lies to any limit.

00:22:08.480 --> 00:22:13.840
He tells lies, then he tries to secretly take away your money,

00:22:14.080 --> 00:22:15.800
take away whatever you have,

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:19.760
all kinds of planning secretive takes place,

00:22:19.960 --> 00:22:22.200
nothing is open,

00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:27.280
and you do it without even understanding.

00:22:28.640 --> 00:22:33.880
But all these people are more interested

00:22:34.520 --> 00:22:39.880
in achieving some sort of a very material advancement,

00:22:40.160 --> 00:22:45.240
whether it is on the right side or the left side.

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:49.240
Many things happen like fundamentalism.

00:22:49.800 --> 00:22:54.520
lf you are a fundamentalist then these bhoots take over

00:22:54.920 --> 00:22:59.040
and they try to overpower you.

00:22:59.360 --> 00:23:01.360
They try to teach you how to

00:23:01.560 --> 00:23:07.160
kill people who do not belong to your religion or to your sect.

00:23:07.360 --> 00:23:13.080
They give ideas and they fight and they quarrel and they kill.

00:23:13.560 --> 00:23:17.480
But the Mother Earth

00:23:18.120 --> 00:23:23.120
or the sea, anything,

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:29.120
any one of these elements can work out the destruction.

00:23:29.560 --> 00:23:32.440
Ln such places you'll find

00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:37.160
big earthquakes taking place and destroying them.

00:23:37.840 --> 00:23:42.200
Or there could be a hurricane that will come and destroy them.

00:23:42.400 --> 00:23:45.960
Of course some innocent people are also killed with them.

00:23:46.480 --> 00:23:52.320
It could be anything that you do wrong,

00:23:54.560 --> 00:23:59.280
it is being corrected by all these five elements.

