Ln lndia we had a place called as Latur

00:24:07.280 --> 00:24:10.960
where people used to drink and drink and drink.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:17.320
Once they went for drinking

00:24:18.360 --> 00:24:24.480
when they had immersed the statue of Shri Ganesha.

00:24:24.680 --> 00:24:30.680
That we do, we put it in the sea,

00:24:30.880 --> 00:24:34.080
after three days, maybe seven days or ten days.

00:24:34.440 --> 00:24:37.280
