00:44:27.080 --> 00:44:30.720
This is the Last Judgement. All right, that's how you'll be judged,

00:44:30.960 --> 00:44:35.920
by your own stupidity you'll be judged.

00:44:37.640 --> 00:44:42.360
l have told so many Sahaja Yogis something small,

00:44:42.560 --> 00:44:44.880
that you must put some oil in the nights

00:44:45.080 --> 00:44:47.240
and the morning time you wash.

00:44:47.440 --> 00:44:49.920
But they don't do it.

00:44:50.360 --> 00:44:55.280
But by doing that what happens is that you soothe yourself,

00:44:55.680 --> 00:44:58.040
you sleep well.

00:44:58.360 --> 00:45:02.080
Oiling is a very good thing. We need it all of us,

00:45:02.280 --> 00:45:04.880
especially in this cold weather, we need it.

00:45:05.160 --> 00:45:07.280
But they won't put it.

00:45:07.600 --> 00:45:09.800
They'll neglect themselves.

00:45:10.000 --> 00:45:11.760
Because they think they're Sahaja Yogis

00:45:11.960 --> 00:45:14.200
they are protected, Mother can oil them.

00:45:14.720 --> 00:45:18.840
It's not so. You have to look after yourself.

00:45:19.480 --> 00:45:25.560
As far as the body is concerned, the mind is concerned,

00:45:39.240 --> 00:45:41.720
you are responsible for your body.

00:45:41.920 --> 00:45:46.640
With Sahaja Yoga you will understand what's wrong with you,

00:45:46.840 --> 00:45:48.400
what you are doing wrong.

00:45:48.600 --> 00:45:51.840
l mean l tell you some things which are very important,

00:45:52.120 --> 00:45:57.920
but to you they may not be, but you should try that.

00:45:58.760 --> 00:46:02.000
As it is you are Realised Souls, your spirit is there,

00:46:02.320 --> 00:46:03.840
you can feel the vibrations,

00:46:04.040 --> 00:46:07.960
and you can understand what's wrong with the person.

00:46:08.600 --> 00:46:13.080
Mostly what l have seen, now it is much less,

00:46:13.520 --> 00:46:18.480
that people only inform me always about people who are possessed.

00:46:18.920 --> 00:46:20.960
''Mother, such and such person is possessed''.

00:46:21.280 --> 00:46:24.000
''Mother this person has got this possession''.

00:46:24.240 --> 00:46:29.920
l said, ''But, throw them out!'' That's all!

00:46:31.840 --> 00:46:34.760
Why do you want me to bother about them?

00:46:34.960 --> 00:46:36.920
Just throw them out!

00:46:37.240 --> 00:46:40.040
Then after going out of Sahaja Yoga they will realise,

00:46:40.240 --> 00:46:42.720
then they will say ''Mother we don't want to go out of Sahaja Yoga''

00:46:42.920 --> 00:46:46.840
Why? Because they know that now

00:46:47.200 --> 00:46:51.920
they are completely away

00:46:52.400 --> 00:46:56.440
from reality and from safety.

00:46:56.840 --> 00:46:59.640
So they want to come back.

00:46:59.840 --> 00:47:03.120
Those who can come back can come back.

00:47:03.320 --> 00:47:07.000
But those who should not come back should never come back.

00:47:07.200 --> 00:47:12.280
Because they are so mad that they'll create a fashion of madness,

00:47:12.800 --> 00:47:15.080
and people can get influenced by that.

00:47:15.440 --> 00:47:21.080
So to get influenced by others is not a sign of a Sahaja Yogi.

00:47:21.640 --> 00:47:23.640
He can influence others,

00:47:23.880 --> 00:47:29.960
but how does he get influenced by others but for Sahaja Yoga?

00:47:30.240 --> 00:47:32.960
Sahaja Yoga is the discriminating power.

00:47:33.160 --> 00:47:35.760
And who has given you this is the Kundalini.

00:47:35.960 --> 00:47:38.840
So this Kundalini which is your mother,

00:47:39.280 --> 00:47:43.600
the one which is now in your triangular bone, also

00:47:43.800 --> 00:47:48.160
gives you all the qualities and all the beauties of your being.

00:47:48.840 --> 00:47:50.800
Of course l have told you so many things about

00:47:51.000 --> 00:47:54.320
Kundalini that l need not tell you.

00:47:54.680 --> 00:47:59.240
But she also can correct the left side.

00:47:59.960 --> 00:48:02.600
Some people have a habit

00:48:02.880 --> 00:48:07.880
of all the time crying and weeping over. l don't know.

00:48:08.360 --> 00:48:11.400
Every time you meet them they are in tears:

00:48:11.840 --> 00:48:13.800
''And what has happened?''

00:48:14.080 --> 00:48:17.160
''Mother this has happened, that has happened'' and all that.

00:48:17.360 --> 00:48:19.720
They write letters after letters to me,

00:48:19.920 --> 00:48:22.880
telling about their woes, their troubles and this and that.

00:48:23.080 --> 00:48:25.280
Baba you are Sahaja Yogis now.

00:48:25.720 --> 00:48:30.040
Now you are in the Garden of Eden,

00:48:30.240 --> 00:48:33.280
you are in the heavens.

00:48:33.920 --> 00:48:36.760
And why are they thinking about all the hellish things

00:48:36.960 --> 00:48:40.200
which are not important? Why?

00:48:41.000 --> 00:48:46.240
Because you haven't got your individuality either.

00:49:09.920 --> 00:49:15.880
Now as Sahaja Yogis you have to develop your discrimination

00:49:16.200 --> 00:49:20.040
of understanding what others are.

00:49:20.280 --> 00:49:22.800
Also about yourself.

00:49:23.040 --> 00:49:27.040
Why do you hanker after things? Try to understand.

00:49:27.640 --> 00:49:30.800
What is so great about it?

00:49:31.000 --> 00:49:34.120
Why do you want to do it?

00:49:34.600 --> 00:49:41.600
Question yourself. ls it some possession?

00:49:42.560 --> 00:49:45.000
ls it some fashion?

00:49:45.440 --> 00:49:51.520
Or is it your individual feeling?

00:49:52.240 --> 00:49:54.800
So, l'm trying to tell you

00:49:55.040 --> 00:50:00.200
that this left side of yours is so protective,

00:50:01.280 --> 00:50:04.280
at the same time

00:50:04.600 --> 00:50:08.080
if you are very aggressive about your left side

00:50:08.720 --> 00:50:14.280
you are thrown from one to another to another to another into hell.

00:50:15.400 --> 00:50:18.400
And then you suffer.

00:50:18.880 --> 00:50:24.840
So you must understand, your wisdom should be there,

00:50:25.240 --> 00:50:29.360
which you can develop very much with the help of the left side.

00:50:29.880 --> 00:50:34.760
Wisdom can be very well developed.

00:50:35.040 --> 00:50:38.880
Now there's somebody, say a Sahaja Yogi, so called,

00:50:39.080 --> 00:50:46.000
and he is absolutely aggressive, money-oriented, deceitful

00:50:46.640 --> 00:50:50.920
and you get into his trap.

00:50:53.000 --> 00:50:56.200
ln Hindi we call it Chakkar, Chakkar.

00:50:56.880 --> 00:51:02.800
And once you get involved into that you go on drifting;

00:51:04.320 --> 00:51:09.320
still your left side will protect, up to a point.

00:51:09.800 --> 00:51:15.240
But if you are too much of it, it throws you ''Get out, get out''.

00:51:16.920 --> 00:51:20.000
Now the time has come for all of us to understand

00:51:20.200 --> 00:51:21.800
that you are all Sahaja Yogis

00:51:22.000 --> 00:51:25.120
and you have a very big responsibility,

00:51:25.640 --> 00:51:30.080
very, very big responsibility that you should do

00:51:30.560 --> 00:51:34.880
what your enlightened conscience tells you.

00:51:35.480 --> 00:51:41.160
Take to your enlightenment and live under that light,

00:51:41.440 --> 00:51:45.040
and don't jump in the darkness.

00:51:45.320 --> 00:51:47.960
And by that you will also understand

00:51:48.160 --> 00:51:52.240
who is the right person and who is not the right person.

00:51:54.320 --> 00:51:58.480
Even in Sahaja Yoga this negativity can work,

00:51:59.120 --> 00:52:01.080
it works.

00:52:01.280 --> 00:52:04.440
And one should not get involved

00:52:04.680 --> 00:52:07.960
into any negative thoughts of others,

00:52:08.520 --> 00:52:13.080
or negative doing of others.

00:52:13.840 --> 00:52:17.200
It's a warning today l wanted to give you all,

00:52:17.880 --> 00:52:20.360
because you people are

00:52:20.560 --> 00:52:26.520
very much there, to enjoy.

00:52:29.280 --> 00:52:34.040
Look after your attention, where does it go.

00:52:34.960 --> 00:52:38.760
There is so many beautiful things, see the flowers, so beautiful!.

00:52:38.960 --> 00:52:40.880
See this thing they have made so beautifully.

00:52:41.080 --> 00:52:44.280
It makes my heart jump with joy;

00:52:44.920 --> 00:52:48.280
while some people don't even notice.

00:52:48.960 --> 00:52:50.080
The other day l asked somebody,

00:52:50.280 --> 00:52:53.960
''Who had made that flower arrangement?'' ''Which flower?''

00:52:54.200 --> 00:52:58.000
l said ''The one that was there'' ''Which one?''

00:52:58.360 --> 00:53:02.040
So l told the names of the flowers. ''We never saw''

00:53:02.280 --> 00:53:05.280
Where were you looking,

00:53:05.760 --> 00:53:08.280
that you couldn't see the flowers?!

00:53:08.800 --> 00:53:10.720
Because your eyes are so stupid

00:53:10.920 --> 00:53:12.920
that they cannot see the beauty.

00:53:13.120 --> 00:53:18.920
They are engulfed with all kinds of negative things.

00:53:19.440 --> 00:53:24.920
So the goddess has to kill all the rakshasas.

00:53:25.440 --> 00:53:30.080
l don't know how many she has killed, and again they are back.

00:53:30.280 --> 00:53:34.280
And again people are being trapped.

00:53:34.680 --> 00:53:37.160
This is going on.

00:53:37.640 --> 00:53:42.200
So these rakshasas are there and you have to pin-point them.

00:53:42.600 --> 00:53:47.200
And tell people ''Where are you going? He's a rakshasa.

00:53:47.400 --> 00:53:52.080
What he has done, what has he achieved?''

00:53:52.440 --> 00:53:56.360
Now you should talk like that;

00:53:58.320 --> 00:54:00.360
openly.

00:54:00.600 --> 00:54:05.120
So you can save many people who are going to these rakshasas,

00:54:05.320 --> 00:54:11.040
who are coming in such clothes that you cannot make them out.

00:54:12.680 --> 00:54:16.920
They will be destroyed, one by one,

00:54:17.200 --> 00:54:18.880
but when they are in the heart

00:54:19.120 --> 00:54:23.040
of so many people how can you destroy them?

00:54:24.360 --> 00:54:27.160
So it is for you people to tell them

00:54:27.400 --> 00:54:30.880
what these rakshasas are doing.

00:54:31.240 --> 00:54:33.240
l know their tricks,

00:54:33.760 --> 00:54:39.160
but the worst part is that the human beings fall into their tricks.

00:54:39.680 --> 00:54:44.840
So you have to be very self-understanding.

00:54:45.560 --> 00:54:48.000
Ask always the question ''Why?

00:54:48.240 --> 00:54:50.960
Why am l attracted to this?

00:54:51.240 --> 00:54:53.040
What is the gain?''

00:54:53.560 --> 00:54:57.200
Ask yourself this question.

00:54:58.280 --> 00:54:59.920
You'll find

00:55:00.200 --> 00:55:03.920
that after coming to Sahaja Yoga you have gained so much.

00:55:04.440 --> 00:55:07.440
So now, why have this false idea?

00:55:07.720 --> 00:55:12.760
why go after false things, negative things?

00:55:13.640 --> 00:55:16.040
That's what Sahaja Yogis have to do,

00:55:16.280 --> 00:55:19.280
because not that they're responsible for others,

00:55:19.520 --> 00:55:22.800
they are responsible for themselves also.

00:55:24.920 --> 00:55:27.360
Now the sweetest thing said about her is

00:55:27.840 --> 00:55:32.200
that she gives you Shraddha.

00:55:33.720 --> 00:55:37.800
Shraddha we can translate it as faith.

00:55:39.000 --> 00:55:44.400
To have faith, rightly not wrongly.

00:55:45.880 --> 00:55:50.360
People take full advantage if you have wrong faiths.

00:55:51.480 --> 00:55:56.640
But faith is very important, that she gives also.

00:55:58.920 --> 00:56:02.280
And that's very joy-giving.

00:56:02.800 --> 00:56:06.000
The faith is very joy-giving.

00:56:06.280 --> 00:56:11.800
But when the incarnations lived, nobody believed in them.

00:56:12.840 --> 00:56:17.040
They had no faith in them. Christ, they crucified,

00:56:17.360 --> 00:56:21.480
nobody stood up to say, ''Why are you crucifying him?''

00:56:22.720 --> 00:56:27.720
All of them; nobody could have

00:56:27.920 --> 00:56:30.920
that faith to stand up.

00:56:31.680 --> 00:56:33.840
They may fight for their own country,

00:56:34.040 --> 00:56:36.280
they may fight for their religion or own nonsense,

00:56:36.880 --> 00:56:41.840
but, ''That a man, this man, is really the Truth,

00:56:42.520 --> 00:56:47.680
he is the one who is an incarnation'', nobody will say it.

00:56:50.760 --> 00:56:53.400
So yesterday l was stunned

00:56:54.080 --> 00:56:57.840
to see the drama they have shown.

00:56:58.280 --> 00:57:01.000
l mean, l couldn't face myself, l should say.

00:57:01.280 --> 00:57:03.280
Though it's the Truth, of course, l agree.

00:57:03.680 --> 00:57:05.880
But l couldn't face myself.

00:57:06.200 --> 00:57:10.000
l am too humble to accept such a thing,

00:57:10.560 --> 00:57:16.080
and it's very ingenious, it's very great to create such a drama

00:57:17.880 --> 00:57:21.280
and of all the things. At first l had said that

00:57:21.640 --> 00:57:24.760
the English have such a sense of drama,

00:57:25.200 --> 00:57:28.280
they had people like Shakespeare and all that,

00:57:28.680 --> 00:57:31.280
and the way they were producing drama l couldn't understand.

00:57:31.600 --> 00:57:34.960
But this one was the last word on perfection.

00:57:35.240 --> 00:57:38.880
So much so that l couldn't say a word about it.

00:57:39.120 --> 00:57:41.920
l was just stunned.

00:57:42.280 --> 00:57:46.000
The Truth that they have propounded.

00:57:46.440 --> 00:57:50.440
But in my lifetime

00:57:50.800 --> 00:57:55.880
you will have no doubts, if you have some sense in you.

00:57:57.000 --> 00:58:00.040
Because so many miracles are taking place.

00:58:00.880 --> 00:58:03.280
Today only somebody told me:

00:58:03.680 --> 00:58:08.280
''Somebody had cancer,

00:58:09.800 --> 00:58:12.800
ulcer and all kinds of things,

00:58:13.440 --> 00:58:17.800
and after Sahaja Yoga she went to the hospital and she had nothing''.

00:58:18.920 --> 00:58:21.800
All such miracles are taking place. Leave alone.

00:58:22.000 --> 00:58:26.120
Also there are never have happened like this

00:58:26.640 --> 00:58:31.280
that there are photographs of mine

00:58:32.840 --> 00:58:36.080
where you see, is remarkable.

00:58:36.720 --> 00:58:39.000
Even the scientists are surprised at it,

00:58:39.280 --> 00:58:43.280
how these photographs are coming.

00:58:44.200 --> 00:58:48.000
Actually there was Shri Ganesha standing behind it actually.

00:58:48.200 --> 00:58:50.960
Only in one camera it came.

00:58:51.400 --> 00:58:55.320
It is just for you people to have faith.

00:58:55.680 --> 00:58:58.760
Because when the person is not there,

00:58:58.960 --> 00:59:02.280
like Christ is no more, now everybody's going to church.

00:59:02.680 --> 00:59:05.920
Shri Rama is not there so they are all singing his praise.

00:59:06.200 --> 00:59:11.280
Shri Krishna is not there so they are ''Hari Rama, Hari Krishna''.

00:59:12.480 --> 00:59:16.880
So when there is Sakshat, when that is before you,

00:59:17.120 --> 00:59:19.280
you don't accept.

00:59:19.800 --> 00:59:23.280
Because perhaps you don't believe you can deserve it, perhaps.

00:59:23.680 --> 00:59:25.960
Or may be it is,

00:59:26.200 --> 00:59:28.880
l don't know, human beings it is very difficult to understand them.

00:59:29.080 --> 00:59:32.000
When you are standing before them they don't believe.

00:59:32.280 --> 00:59:34.280
When you are no more, then they will believe.

00:59:34.760 --> 00:59:37.280
It is a very funny thing, isn't it?

00:59:37.720 --> 00:59:40.800
All through out if you see the history of spirituality

00:59:41.000 --> 00:59:43.920
this has been going on.

00:59:44.840 --> 00:59:49.320
Gyanadeva showed some miracles, still

00:59:50.640 --> 00:59:53.360
only the wise, only the sensible

00:59:53.920 --> 00:59:56.960
could understand and believe it.

00:59:57.200 --> 01:00:00.200
And there is so few that as a result

01:00:00.400 --> 01:00:04.440
such people are crucified, killed or done anything.

01:00:06.440 --> 01:00:08.440
They have tried that with me,

01:00:08.880 --> 01:00:14.120
but you know in this life l have come in all Forms,

01:00:14.440 --> 01:00:17.000
and nobody can destroy me:

01:00:17.200 --> 01:00:22.080
Unless and until l want to finish myself, no one can.

01:00:23.240 --> 01:00:27.680
The powers are of love, affection, compassion,

01:00:27.920 --> 01:00:32.080
but also there's a power

01:00:32.720 --> 01:00:37.240
which completely corrects other people.

01:00:38.680 --> 01:00:41.880
So

01:00:42.440 --> 01:00:45.600
to you people not to have faith in Sahaja Yoga

01:00:46.200 --> 01:00:49.200
shows complete blankness,

01:00:49.520 --> 01:00:51.080
you have seen the photographs,

01:00:51.280 --> 01:00:54.080
you have seen everything, you have known the miracles,

01:00:54.280 --> 01:00:58.000
it has happened to you. You have the experience of Sahaja Yoga.

01:00:58.400 --> 01:01:02.400
Despite that your faith is so weak.

01:01:02.600 --> 01:01:05.080
She's the one who gives you faith,

01:01:05.280 --> 01:01:08.880
so you have to praise her, you have to fall at her feet,

01:01:09.080 --> 01:01:12.200
you have to worship her and ask her

01:01:12.520 --> 01:01:15.280
''Oh Mother, give us that faith''.

01:01:15.560 --> 01:01:17.920
And with this faith you'll be amazed,

01:01:18.200 --> 01:01:20.360
any person who has this kind of a faith,

01:01:20.560 --> 01:01:23.440
he tells me ''Mother, please, do this''

01:01:23.920 --> 01:01:27.240
It happens. It just happens.

01:01:27.640 --> 01:01:34.280
Such right they have got to ask for anything. It works out.

01:01:34.520 --> 01:01:38.000
But first your faith should be solid.

01:01:38.280 --> 01:01:40.000
Faith should be real.

01:01:40.240 --> 01:01:45.720
lf it is real and if it is deep,

01:01:45.920 --> 01:01:48.280
you can achieve whatever you want.

01:01:48.640 --> 01:01:52.040
Not wrong, but good things.

01:01:52.280 --> 01:01:55.800
And so try to develop that faith

01:01:56.000 --> 01:02:00.920
and as a faith gives you such joy and happiness,

01:02:01.160 --> 01:02:04.760
you get committed, you get involved,

01:02:04.960 --> 01:02:08.280
and you don't want to get out of it.

01:02:08.680 --> 01:02:12.360
So the greatest thing is the blessing

01:02:13.000 --> 01:02:16.880
of the left side is the faith.

01:02:17.120 --> 01:02:19.840
Faith which is pure,

01:02:20.040 --> 01:02:25.960
faith can be translated as, we can say, Vishwas

01:02:26.200 --> 01:02:30.240
but not. Faith is Shraddha.

01:02:30.480 --> 01:02:36.160
Shraddha means something that is within;

01:02:37.120 --> 01:02:40.040
which has no doubts,

01:02:40.240 --> 01:02:43.800
which has no doing as such, it is just there.

01:02:44.000 --> 01:02:47.280
So you should now develop faith

01:02:47.520 --> 01:02:51.680
about yourself and about Sahaja Yoga.

01:02:51.920 --> 01:02:57.040
lf your faith is strong you will see many miracles also.

01:02:57.400 --> 01:03:00.400
But with miracles, with everything,

01:03:00.920 --> 01:03:03.440
still if you don't understand

01:03:03.960 --> 01:03:08.960
then it is your discretion.

01:03:10.080 --> 01:03:16.000
May God Bless You.

